# Model Routing Logic
- IF MODEL == "Gemini 3 Flash" OR "GPT-5.4 Mini": 
  - Focus on: Syntax, CSS, simple Vue components, and Docker commands.
  - Style: Be concise. Don't over-analyze.
- IF MODEL == "Codex 5.1 Mini":
  - Focus on: Backend logic (Express), SQL queries (MySQL), and complex Vue computed properties.
  - Target: Professional, clean code.
- IF MODEL == "Gemini 3.1 Pro":
  - Focus on: Azure Architecture, SISPACTOS integration, Keycloak security flows, and RIPS/DNP compliance logic.
  - Style: Deep analysis, check for edge cases and security vulnerabilities.